On the flip side, WW dragons give HUGE kromzek hits.  Guildmate went from below the negative cap with Kromzek to ally in about 12 hours in WW.  ToV west doesn't give very big hits, and HoT has no faction.<br>
Kael arena is the best spot for CoV.  Tag along on raids, back when we were doing Kael arena we didn't mind if anyone wanted to join us, as long as they stayed out of the way.<br>
Quest givers behind tormax are GREAT for Yelinak faction (we HAD to do this prior to SS quest givers being on CoV)<br>
2-3 Quest Giver runs and you'll be amiably+ to Yelinak... but you'll also be max kos to tormax in case your guild should change their mind about where you want to hunt. <p><br><center>
