<br>
Group:  Warrior (Heavey tank), Cleric, dr00d, Chanter, wiz/mage, wiz/mage.<br>
<br>
Warr run around the entire zone inclueing the fort collecting the giants.  Warrior brings back 20 giants to the wiz spires.  Casters run in and AoE.  Giants go down so fast it is not even funny.  Scilination (sp?) the giants to death you will see the scrolls of faction roll by like crazy.<br>
